class="block-intro-text"><p>Adobe Illustrator is a powerful vector-based design application that is the industry standard for creating logos. Anyone with basic knowledge of the application can use the program to create professional-looking logos in under ninety minutes.</p><p>Our step-by-step guide will help you understand the basic elements that make up a logo and how you can use them to create a unique visual identity for your business. If you don't have Illustrator, you can still create a stunning logo using our <a
href="https://www.notzarla.com/free-logo-maker">free logo maker</a>.</p></div></div></div></div><div
