</span><p>"Raster Effects" is set to "High (300 ppi)" for optimal image resolution.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section2" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>2.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=setting-up-your-workspace>Setting up your workspace.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section2-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=switch-your-workspace>Switch your workspace.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-switch-your-workspace-288x288-2021093.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Switch your workspace."></div></div><p>Once you've created your document, select the "Painting" workspace from the drop-down menu of the "Switch Workspace" icon in the top-right corner.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section2-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=create-a-save-file>Create a save file.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-save-file-288x288-2021093.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Create a save file."></div></div><p>It's important to save your Illustrator document regularly to avoid losing any work.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
