class="section-title">
<span>5.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=creating-an-icon>Creating an icon.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section5-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=decide-on-an-icon-for-your-logo>Decide on an icon for your logo.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-decide-on-an-icon-for-your-logo-288x288-2021092_2021-09-03-104343_jiqd.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Decide on an icon for your logo."></div></div><p>An icon is an image or symbol that will give your business a brand identity. Think of something that captures the nature and values of your business and gather some reference images. For this example, we're going to construct a cloud icon using various shapes.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section5-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=create-a-new-layer>Create a new layer.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
