 the corners.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Click and drag the small circular handle inside the corners of the square toward the center of the shape until you're happy with the roundness of the corners.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator#how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section3-step4","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-soften-the-corners-288x288-2021093.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}}]},{"@type":"HowToSection","position":"4","name":"<p>Adding color.<\/p>\n","itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"1","name":"<p>Choose a color scheme for your logo.<\/p>\n","text":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.zarla.com\/guides\/logo-colors\">Colors in logos<\/a> play an important role in the branding of your business. Colors have certain psychological associations and effects on people and can help give your brand a defining character.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator#how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section4-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-choose-a-color-scheme-for-your-logo-288x288-2021093.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Set the stroke color.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>In the top-left of the menu bar, set the \"Stroke\" color to \"[None].\"<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator#how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section4-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-set-the-stroke-color-288x288-2021093.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>You can add color to give your shape an outline and change the thickness and style of the stroke in the top menu bar.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"3","name":"<p>Set the fill color.<\/