roke\" to \"[None].\"<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p>Change the transparency by adjusting the \"Opacity\" to 50% in the top menu bar.<\/p>\n"}]}]},{"@type":"HowToSection","position":"8","name":"<p>Making elements fit.<\/p>\n","itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"1","name":"<p>Make the shadow fit into the shape.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>In order to complete the shape of the shadow, we need to make it fit within the icon border and around the bottom of the cloud.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator#how-to-make-a-logo-in-illustrator-section8-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-make-the-shadow-fit-into-the-shape-288x288-2021093.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p>Click on the \"Selection Tool (V)\" icon in the left menu bar.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p>Select the blue square shape by clicking on the small circle to the right of the layer icon in the layers panel.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p>Click on \"Edit\" in the main menu bar and select \"Copy\" from the drop-down menu.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p>Select the shadow shape in the layers panel and click on \"Edit\" in the menu bar and click on \"Paste in Back.\"<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p>Hold down \"Shift\" and click on the shadow shape so that both objects are selected.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p>Finally, click on the \"Pathfinder\" icon in the right menu bar and select the \"Intersect\" option.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>This will contain the shadow to the borders of the square icon.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Make the shadow fit around the icon.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>In order to make the shadow fit the outline of the cloud, we will use a similar process.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notza